---
import Layout from "@layout/layout.astro";
import Separator from "@components/separator.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me - ~/isidrok"
  description="Learn more about Isidro Torregrosa - Technical Lead & Senior Full-Stack Engineer"
  type="website"
  canonicalURL={Astro.url.href}
>
  <article class="container">
    <header class="intro">
      <h1>Hi There!</h1>
      <Separator />
    </header>

    <section class="content">
      <p>
        I’m <b>Isidro Torregrosa Torralba</b>, a Lead Engineer based in Spain.
        Over the past <b>9+ years</b>, I’ve specialized in building products end
        to end. I’m primarily focused on <b>TypeScript</b>, <b>Node.js</b>, and <b
          >web development</b
        >
        — but I’m happy working across any stack that helps solve the problem, including
        AI tooling and LLMs.
      </p>

      <p>
        I’m increasingly drawn to companies using technology for positive
        impact. If you’re working on meaningful problems or interesting
        technical challenges, I’d love to connect. You can find more details
        about my experience in <a
          href="/isidro-torregrosa-cv.pdf"
          target="_blank">my CV</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
